501
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:59,350
Hati-hati.

502
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:01,430
Terima kasih, Guo Xu.

503
00:26:01,430 --> 00:26:03,040
Hati-hati.

504
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:04,830
Aku ambilkan punya kita bertiga.

505
