550
00:27:43,280 --> 00:27:44,230
Koperku berat, tidak?

551
00:27:45,160 --> 00:27:46,430
Koperku berat, tidak?

552
00:27:46,430 --> 00:27:47,350
Tidak, masih oke.

553
00:27:47,350 --> 00:27:48,160
