633
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:48,230
Kita berdua...

634
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:49,110
Aku harus istirahat sebentar.

635
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:50,830
Punyamu sudah pergi satu

636
00:30:50,830 --> 00:30:52,520
