650
00:31:19,230 --> 00:31:20,680
Hatiku rasanya campur aduk,

651
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:23,280
lalu...

652
00:31:30,430 --> 00:31:31,470
(Waktunya makan siang)
Ayo, kita makan.

653
00:31:31,470 --> 00:31:32,520
Ayo, makan.

654
00:31:34,230 --> 00:31:35,280
Akhirnya, aku melihat daging.

655
00:31:36,040 --> 00:31:36,950
Ada daging hari ini.

656
00:31:36,950 --> 00:31:38,350
Baiklah, ayo, makan.

657
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,400
(Mode pamer makan diaktifkan)

658
00:31:40,950 --> 00:31:42,430
Makan lebih banyak lagi, Guo Xu.

659
00:31:42,430 --> 00:31:43,680
Porsi makan mereka terlalu sedikit.

660
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:45,590
Ini semua cuma seporsi bagimu.

661
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,280
Benar, 'kan?

662
00:31:48,190 --> 00:31:50,950
Kenapa hari ini makannya

663
00:31:50,950 --> 00:31:52,310
