664
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:54,880
Kelak, setiap kali makan akan terasa aneh.

665
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,560
Lihatlah, mereka di sana baru mulai seru.

666
00:31:56,560 --> 00:31:58,470
Di sana sangat seru.

667
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,920
