Kau terlalu meremehkanku.

684
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:43,280
Sepertinya iya.

685
00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:44,520
Kau tidak sampai, 'kan?

686
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:46,710
